title: Ranji Trophy: Assam's Syed Mohammad rattles holders Karnataka
text: Veteran left-arm spinner Jamaluddin Syed Mohammad registered his best first-class bowling figures to single-handedly give Assam an upperhand against defending champions Karnataka on the opening day of their Group A Ranji Trophy cricket match here today. Â»
